Input
* Please format "Line 1" and "Line 2" in <<bold>> (e.g. "Line 1" becomes "<<Line 1>>").

Output
* Please fix the typo: "containting" => "containing".

* Please change "long" to "duration".

* Please delete "also".

Constraints
* Please change "some words in English" to "may contain space characters."

* Please add "and [[time1]] < [[time2]]" to the end of the third constraint.

Cases
* Validators 2,3,4 and Tests 3,4: There are wrong input times where [[time1]] ≥ [[time2]], e.g.

Validator 2: Can You Feel The Love Tonight 17:10:00 17:10:00

Test 3: Total Eclipse Of The Heart 17:50:55 17:17:09

Please fix all five cases.

Thanks.
Many thanks for your help. All of the above have been corrected.
